## ü§ù Contributing & Onboarding

- All new devs and partners: Start with the Runbook, and update documentation for any new feature, schema, or process.
- Use PRs for any change to `/supabase/`, `/scripts/`, or core policies.
- All code and operational changes must pass QA and audit review.

